15namespace rtc {
16
17const char* NetworkPreferenceToString(NetworkPreference preference) {
18 switch (preference) {
19 case NetworkPreference::NEUTRAL:
20 return "NEUTRAL";
21 case NetworkPreference::NOT_PREFERRED:
22 return "NOT_PREFERRED";
23 }
24 RTC_CHECK_NOTREACHED();
25}

28NetworkMonitorInterface::~NetworkMonitorInterface() {}
